properties.description: ADF connection to SQL server Development

typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		EMP_ID as decimal(38,18),
		LOGIN_NAME as string,
		FULL_NAME as string,
		EMP_TYPE_ID as decimal(38,18),
		GROUP_ID as decimal(38,18),
		DEPT_ID as decimal(38,18),
		LOC_ID as decimal(38,18),
		SYND_ID as decimal(38,18),
		DISABLED_IND as decimal(38,18),
		LOGGING_IND as decimal(38,18),
		UNDERWRITER_IND as decimal(38,18),
		CLAIMS_ADJUSTER_IND as decimal(38,18),
		REMINDER_RESP_IND as string,
		PASSWORD_DATE as timestamp,
		CREATED_BY as string,
		CREATED_WHEN as timestamp,
		UPDATED_BY as string,
		UPDATED_WHEN as timestamp,
		PERSONAL_CLAIMS_IND as decimal(38,18),
		NEW_LOGIN_NAME as string,
		E_MAIL as string,
		PROMAN_EKEY as decimal(38,18),
		JOBNAME as string,
		UNDERWRITER_ASSISTANT_IND as decimal(38,18),
		OLD_LOGIN_NAME as string,
		AUTHORIZED_PAYMENT_LEVEL_ID as decimal(38,18)
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> emp
source(output(
		INCIDENT_ID as decimal(38,18),
		UNIQUE_ENTRY_ID as decimal(38,18),
		INCIDENT_FILE_NUMBER as decimal(38,18),
		CLAIM_TYPE_ID_MAIN_CLAIM_TYPE as decimal(38,18),
		EMPLOYEE_ID_MAIN_ADJUSTER as decimal(38,18),
		MEMBERS_REFERENCE as string,
		ARCHIVE_NUMBER as decimal(38,18),
		ARCHIVE_DATE as timestamp,
		OLD_ARCHIVE_NUMBER as decimal(38,18),
		OLD_ARCHIVE_DATE as timestamp,
		GEOGRAPHICAL_AREA_ID_PLACE as decimal(38,18),
		GEOGRAPHICAL_AREA_ID_VOY_FROM as decimal(38,18),
		GEOGRAPHICAL_AREA_ID_VOY_TO as decimal(38,18),
		DATE_OF_INCIDENT as timestamp,
		MONTH_OR_PERIOD_OF_INCIDENT as string,
		CASUALTY_ID as decimal(38,18),
		MAIN_CAUSE_ID as decimal(38,18),
		GEOGRAPHICAL_AREA_ID_MAIN_JUR as decimal(38,18),
		CURRENCY_ID_MAIN_CURRENCY as decimal(38,18),
		INCIDENT_TEXT as string,
		EMPLOYEE_ID_REGISTERED_BY as decimal(38,18),
		REGISTERED_DATE as timestamp,
		LAST_REVIEWED_DATE as timestamp,
		LARGE_CLAIMS_GROUP_INDICATOR as string,
		TOTAL_CURRENT_RESERVE_USD as double,
		TOTAL_CURRENT_COMP_USD as double,
		CREATED_BY as string,
		CREATED_WHEN as timestamp,
		UPDATED_BY as string,
		UPDATED_WHEN as timestamp,
		TIMESTAMP_ as decimal(38,18),
		OFFICE_ROLE_ID_REFUND as decimal(38,18),
		REFUND_PERCENT as decimal(38,18),
		REFUND_MAPPER_NUMBER as decimal(38,18),
		PHYSICAL_FILE_CREATED as decimal(38,18),
		GEOGRAPHICAL_AREA_ID_1ST_PORT as decimal(38,18),
		TIMEBAR as timestamp,
		DEALT_WITH as string,
		OM_CLAIM_TYPE as decimal(38,18),
		COMPLEXITY_ID as double,
		NO_ICR_REMINDER_DATE as timestamp,
		EVENT_ID as double,
		EVENT_DETAIL_ID as double,
		MAIN_CLAIM_DETAIL_ID as double,
		MYGARD_CLAIM_ID as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> inc
source(output(
		SYND_ID as decimal(38,18),
		SYND_NAME as string,
		CREATED_BY as string,
		CREATED_WHEN as timestamp,
		UPDATED_BY as string,
		UPDATED_WHEN as timestamp
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> syn
source(output(
		SOURCE_CODE_KEY as string,
		SOURCE_SYSTEM as string,
		TARGET_CODE as string,
		TARGET_DESCRIPTION as string,
		CODE_TYPE as string,
		CODE_TYPE_ID as double,
		CODE2 as string,
		OM_X_REF as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> tcross
tcross filter(SOURCE_SYSTEM == 'GIC' && CODE_TYPE_ID ==792) ~> Filter1
emp select(mapColumn(
		EMP_ID,
		SYND_ID
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> emp1
DerivedColumn3 select(mapColumn(
		EMPLOYEE_ID_MAIN_ADJUSTER
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> inc1
DerivedColumn4 select(mapColumn(
		SYND_ID,
		SYND_NAME
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> syn1
DerivedColumn2, inc1 join(EMP_ID == EMPLOYEE_ID_MAIN_ADJUSTER,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'both')~> Join1
Join1, syn1 join(DerivedColumn2@SYND_ID == syn1@SYND_ID,
	joinType:'inner',
	partitionBy('roundRobin', 2),
	broadcast: 'both')~> Join2
Join2, Filter1 join(toString(syn1@SYND_ID) == SOURCE_CODE_KEY,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'both')~> Join3
Join3 select(mapColumn(
		EMP_ID,
		SYND_ID = syn1@SYND_ID,
		SYND_NAME,
		TARGET_CODE,
		TARGET_DESCRIPTION
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Select1
Select1 aggregate(groupBy(TARGET_CODE,
		TARGET_DESCRIPTION,
		SYND_ID,
		EMP_ID),
	SYND_NAME = first(SYND_NAME)) ~> dedup
dedup derive(TEM_KEY = case(isNull(TARGET_CODE), concat('C', toString(SYND_ID)), TARGET_CODE),
		PK_PRE_DIM_CLAIM_TEAM = concat('G', toString(EMP_ID)),
		TEM_DESCRIPTION = case(isNull(TARGET_DESCRIPTION), SYND_NAME, TARGET_DESCRIPTION),
		DATE_INSERTED = currentTimestamp(),
		DATE_LAST_UPDATED = currentTimestamp(),
		INSERTED_BY = 'M_PRE_DIM_CLAIM_TEAM',
		LAST_UPDATED_BY = 'M_PRE_DIM_CLAIM_TEAM') ~> DerivedColumn1
DerivedColumn1 select(mapColumn(
		EMP_ID,
		TEM_KEY,
		PK_PRE_DIM_CLAIM_TEAM,
		TEM_DESCRIPTION,
		DATE_INSERTED,
		DATE_LAST_UPDATED,
		INSERTED_BY,
		LAST_UPDATED_BY
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Select2
emp1 derive(EMP_ID = toInteger(EMP_ID),
		SYND_ID = toInteger(SYND_ID)) ~> DerivedColumn2
inc derive(EMPLOYEE_ID_MAIN_ADJUSTER = toInteger(EMPLOYEE_ID_MAIN_ADJUSTER)) ~> DerivedColumn3
syn derive(SYND_ID = toInteger(SYND_ID)) ~> DerivedColumn4
Select2 sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	partitionFileNames:['M_PRE_DIM_PERBEN'],
	partitionBy('hash', 1),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> sink1
